Robert Douglas (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robert_Douglas_(actor) 0 Robert Douglas (born Robert Douglas Finlayson, 9 November 1909 – 11 January 1999) was an English stage and film actor, a television director and producer.
